1. *Prve* godine studija bile su najteže. (The first years of study were the hardest.)
2. Ona je *prva* završila vježbu. (She was the first to finish the exercise.)
3. *Prvo* mjesto na takmičenju osvojio je on. (He won the first place in the competition.)
4. Njegov *prvi* pokušaj nije uspio. (His first attempt failed.)
5. Ona je *prvom* polažila ispit. (She was the first to pass the exam.)